utral-200 hover:underline">MistralDetector API</a>. For minimal quick-start=
 examples, see <a href=3D"https://deepwiki.com/ai-forever/gigacheck/2.2-qui=
ck-start" class=3D"text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:underline"=
>Quick Start</a>.</p>
