ing-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">RuntimeError: C=
UDA out of memory
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong> Try using a different GPU with <code class=3D=
"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] text-xs font-normal lead=
ing-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">--device "cuda:=
1"</code> or switch to CPU with <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] px-[=
0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden afte=
r:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">--device "cpu"</code>. For large texts, cons=
ider truncating input length.</p>
<p><strong>Issue 3: Missing configuration fields</strong></p>
<pre class=3D"px-2 py-1.5 has-[code]:rounded-md has-[code]:!bg-[#e5e5e5] ha=
s-[div]:bg-transparent has-[div]:!p-0 has-[code]:text-stone-900 dark:has-[c=
