ing-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">AttributeError:=
 'Config' object has no attribute 'with_detr'
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong> The model checkpoint may be from an older ver=
sion. Ensure you're using a model trained with the current codebase version=
.</p>
